---
<section id="ods" class="mx-auto mt-32 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-40 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
    <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-eco-green">Proposito social</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-balance">Tecnologia con proposito social</p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-600">EcoRuta contribuye directamente a los Objetivos de Desarrollo Sostenible de la ONU.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
    <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <div class="mb-6 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-eco-green text-white font-bold">11</div>
          Ciudades y Comunidades Sostenibles
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">Infraestructura inteligente para gestion de residuos urbanos. Mejor servicio publico para todos.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <div class="mb-6 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-eco-green text-white font-bold">13</div>
          Accion por el Clima
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">Reduccion directa de emisiones de CO2: 129 kg diarios, equivalentes a 47 toneladas anuales.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <div class="mb-6 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-eco-green text-white font-bold">12</div>
          Produccion y Consumo Responsables
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">Datos para decisiones informadas sobre generacion y recoleccion de residuos.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm/6 text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full ring-1 ring-gray-900/10">
        <span class="flex size-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-eco-green text-white text-xs font-bold">9</span>
        Industria, Innovacion e Infraestructura
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm/6 text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full ring-1 ring-gray-900/10">
        <span class="flex size-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-eco-green text-white text-xs font-bold">3</span>
        Salud y Bienestar
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
